@startuml
title Viaverse Job Completion / Commission / Payout — Sequence Diagram

participant "marketplace-service" as Marketplace
participant "monetization-service" as Monetization
participant "pricing/config-service" as Config
participant "payment-service" as Payment
database "ledger/accounting" as Ledger
participant "payout provider" as Payout
participant "trust/reporting" as Trust
queue "Outbox / Kafka" as Kafka

Marketplace -> Monetization : JobCompleted event
Monetization -> Config : load fee rules\ncommission %5 default
Monetization -> Payment : read captured amount
Monetization -> Monetization : calculate platform fee + net payout
Monetization -> Ledger : record fee/receivable/payable
Monetization -> Payment : create payout instruction
Payment -> Payout : execute payout
Monetization -> Trust : monetization signals\nnon-ranking sensitive summary
Monetization -> Kafka : CommissionCharged / PayoutCalculated

note bottom
monetization-service calculates business rules;
payment-service moves money;
ledger/accounting records financial truth.
Avoid calculating fees inside marketplace-service.
end note
@enduml
